    "description": {
      "value": "<p>A powerful improved version of the classic Uchiha fireball technique, you fire a flaming orb that travels up to the technique's range (your choice) as a line attack, then explodes. Creatures caught in the explosive Burst take 7d6 fire damage, while creatures only caught in the Line take half as much damage.</p>\n\n<hr><p><b>Empower:</b> Spend 1 Chakra to increase the damage by 1d6, up to 1d6 per level of 18d6 (whichever is lower).</p>\n<p><b>Mastery:</b> Increase the range by 5 ft per step, or increase the radius of the Burst by 5 ft per two steps (chosen when performing).</p>\n",
